-- Electricite de France, Areva Sign Uranium Agreement
-- B y   S t e v e   R h i n d s
-- 2012-02-13T09:09:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-13/electricite-de-france-areva-sign-uranium-agreement-correct-.html
(Corrects period of contract in first paragraph of this
story published Feb. 10)  Areva SA will supply Electricite de
 France  SA with as much as 20,000 metric tons of uranium over the
period 2014 through 2030, the companies said in an e-mailed
statement today.  EDF may also help finance a new mining project with Areva,
according to the statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Steve Rhinds in Paris at 
 srhinds@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
